{"tid":2038462,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"調查：僅五成僱員獲加人工 零售旅業遭減薪 IT界續跑贏大市","createTime":"2020-05-27T14:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T09:04:14.000Z","uid":85524,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fd49c43b3ab8ada641995e240346b904f913dedc","tid":2038462,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T14:44:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E5%83%85%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E5%83%B1%E5%93%A1%E7%8D%B2%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5-%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E6%97%85%E6%A5%AD%E9%81%AD%E6%B8%9B%E8%96%AA-it%E7%95%8C%E7%BA%8C%E8%B7%91%E8%B4%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%82-214500311.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E5%2583%2585%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2583%25B1%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%258A%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E9%259B%25B6%25E5%2594%25AE%25E6%2597%2585%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B8%259B%25E8%2596%25AA-it%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25BA%258C%25E8%25B7%2591%25E8%25B4%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B8%2582-214500311.html&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32RSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=b84f1f21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E5%83%85%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E5%83%B1%E5%93%A1%E7%8D%B2%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5-%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E6%97%85%E6%A5%AD%E9%81%AD%E6%B8%9B%E8%96%AA-it%E7%95%8C%E7%BA%8C%E8%B7%91%E8%B4%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%82-214500311.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年經濟轉差，有求職平台機構發表薪酬調查，顯示今年僅五成受訪僱員獲得加薪，較去年減少兩成，今年平均加薪增幅僅百分之一點三，遠低於去年調查所得的百分之五點一。零售及旅遊業僱員慘遭減薪，另有四成來自不同行業的僱員要凍薪，多達七成五受訪者對就業前景感到負面態度，並表明有意轉工。<br />\n<br />\n四千名打工仔今年三月回覆網上問卷調查，四成打工仔今年凍薪，逾三成來自零售業和旅遊款待受訪者要減薪。<span style=\"color: red;\">加薪方面，以從事資訊科技及分析或策略的僱員薪酬增長幅度最高，分別達百分之六點一及百分之五點八；其中資訊科技已連續數年高於平均加幅，反映行業依然發展迅速，對人才需求殷切。</span><br />\n<br />\n調查顯示，大部分受訪者主要擔心本港經濟或社會狀況，故對本港就業前景持負面態度；亦有七成八人擔心疫情影響，本港面臨經濟衰退；六成七人憂慮外圍因素不明朗；六成一受訪者預測部分公司或會倒閉而憂慮。有近兩成受訪者因工作前景每況愈下而想轉行，當中從事酒店及旅遊丶客戶服務和綜合管理業受訪者最想轉行。<br />\n<br />\n機構倡網上學習 應戰就業危機<br />\n<br />\n機構認為疫市下打工仔或需考慮兼職工作，而求職者考慮轉工及轉行時應以個人興趣及能力為大前提，避免只專注於薪金及福利，又提醒打工仔可網上學習做好準備，當身處行業危機時可靈活應對。"},{"pid":"897cd85723c6743c435c3caae8caacd23ae6ac02","tid":2038462,"uid":116396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:33:34.000Z","msg":"全民it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff33f8c57fec35b8cfe38fae4967bba64edba687","tid":2038462,"uid":55011,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:41:05.000Z","msg":"IT又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa62a35fd19e21b3492e1d9afd287a68e00d8d3","tid":2038462,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:43:01.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"0fcb7fe9e2a2093cb8bfb540591e6d2a83e0446f","tid":2038462,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:46:03.000Z","msg":"連登仔話齋 : 「加人工  = 食相差」 <br />\n<br />\nIT 狗食相真係好差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔怪得無女啦"},{"pid":"537b0de0be3f681180cf0a0d6b89ee5dfa59ec02","tid":2038462,"uid":254450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:53:58.000Z","msg":"又吹奏IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等陣又會有一大批我冇讀過IT點入行po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b4aa981a2ee6fb3675ff79fa886c7d60aa942d","tid":2038462,"uid":7253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:07:49.000Z","msg":"即係幾年後又it 泡沫爆破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101321b7cbb2718993e630d4ab49d002d5eb423d","tid":2038462,"uid